{"tid":600544,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老餅同事返工成日唔撚帶錢","createTime":"2018-03-21T11:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T06:46:48.000Z","uid":104965,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc70254d7552cc7ee1ba0da8b9737be6e100fbd4","tid":600544,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"食飯無八達通既地方又問你借錢<br />\n<br />\n買少少野返公司又借<br />\n<br />\n買野叫Courier 又話唔記得㩒錢比人<br />\n<br />\n最煩係自己買個袋都想問你借<br />\n<br />\n咁我當然唔撚借，話無咁多錢<br />\n<br />\n佢扮曬野：oh 估唔到你仲窮過我<br />\n<br />\n我唔想借比你咋老閪殼！<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠唔借錢比我唔通我有錢過佢呀？<br />\n<br />\n我好憎同事間太多錢銀瓜葛<br />\n<br />\n雖然數目唔係多 但係成撚日要記好9 煩<br />\n<br />\n你又唔撚係即日比番我喎！<br />\n<br />\n同你好撚熟？<br />\n<br />\n帶錢返工啦仆街！"},{"pid":"2c97d5054bdb3cd7706a59ff463fbe881caa0a9e","tid":600544,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲返工會袋幾多$？<br />\n小弟通常500 內"},{"pid":"e6fc2ba9070e405ada2aa93144dab7ff452ea1e1","tid":600544,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c97d5054bdb3cd7706a59ff463fbe881caa0a9e","tid":600544,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲返工會袋幾多$？<br />\n小弟通常500 內"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"500乜都夠啦，食飯夾錢payme / credit card , 又有八達通"},{"pid":"bf876d89011fce402df86b61bbcc0e9b084fe28e","tid":600544,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"食禁400袋，八達通入200<br />\n少於100先再禁"},{"pid":"88cdbfe11b76e079e194c5803055090673278b94","tid":600544,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccbab299f90031620f88a709ffa1c2db0f9c3b68","tid":600544,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eddda37ebcccfbaf1badcac6392db4055aeeae3","tid":600544,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy